meta.query: SELECT "natica_fitsfile"."id", "natica_fitsfile"."extras", "natica_fitsfile"."md5sum", "natica_fitsfile"."filesize", "natica_fitsfile"."proposal_id", "natica_fitsfile"."ra", "natica_fitsfile"."dec", "natica_fitsfile"."exposure", "natica_fitsfile"."archive_filename", "natica_fitsfile"."date_obs", "natica_fitsfile"."original_filename", "natica_fitsfile"."release_date", "natica_fitsfile"."instrument", "natica_fitsfile"."telescope" FROM "natica_fitsfile" ORDER BY "natica_fitsfile"."original_filename" ASC LIMIT 100
